		</RichText>
		<RichText x="972" y="974" width="121" height="44" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.6">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffcc99">Base ATK：<br/><span fontSize="18" color="#dddddd">6.6</span><span fontSize="18" color="#e599ff">B2</span></p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#7fbfff" distance="0" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="599" y="115" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="722" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">Battle-Hardened Precursor’s Secret Source Control Array: <br/>Will of the Hive</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#7fbfff" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="67" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#2c62d3" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#2c62d3">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="698" width="498" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">厚度等于<span color="#ffdfbf">100%</span><span>先驱阵列生命值，展开后持续</span><span color="#ffdfbf">20s</span><span>，使重力大幅下降并</span><span color="#ffdfbf">-45%</span><span>跳跃速度。展开护盾后5s将部署</span><span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>，并持续附着</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span> 持续时间延长至</span><span color="#ffdfbf">45s</span><span>；触发</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">星超导</span><span>反应，或受到</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">星超导</span><span>伤害时，每次减少</span><span color="#ffdfbf">4%</span><span>白盾。白盾存在期间，先驱阵列受到的</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">星超导</span><span>伤害提升</span><span color="#ffdfbf">150%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="73" y="336" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">正常</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="73" y="451" width="46" height="40" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">力场<br/><span fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="12" color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="73" y="396" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="46" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">力场</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="72" y="516" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="47" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p textAlign="center" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">瘫痪</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<Group d:userLabel="ICON__FRAME" d:type="layer" visible="false">
			<Rect x="640" y="832" width="128" height="128" alpha="1" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
				<fill>
					<SolidColor color="#ffffff"/>
				</fill>
			</Rect>
			<Rect x="992" y="832" width="128" height="128" alpha="1" blendMode="normal" radiusX="0" radiusY="0">
