				</fill>
			</Rect>
		</Group>
		<RichText x="66" y="672" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="87" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">力场护盾：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="806" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="87" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">探侦机关：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="832" width="508" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">由先驱阵列召唤，共4枚，每枚拥有<span color="#7fbfff">6水</span><span>盾。将其</span><span color="#ffdfbf">冻结</span><span>后，触发</span><span color="#ffdfbf">超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">星超导</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">碎冰</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">融化</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">结晶</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffdfbf">扩散</span><span>反应会立即将其破坏；部署后，该机关将上升，最终高度约4m，两两分布于先驱阵列后侧的半圆扇区。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5)</span><span> 机关厚度翻倍至</span><span color="#7fbfff">12水</span><span>，且每破坏一枚机关，先驱阵列的</span><span textDecoration="underline">力场护盾</span><span>就减少</span><span color="#ffdfbf">1/8</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="986" width="497" height="39" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">若时限内未击破所有机关，其将进入回收阶段，并根据回收剩余的<span textDecoration="underline">探侦机关</span><span>，获得厚度为</span><span color="#ffdfbf">(12+6×回收数量)</span><span>的</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>护罩。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="960" fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="107" height="26" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="MiSans" fontSize="20" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">水元素护罩：</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
